<li><a href="http://www.designprinciplesftw.com/">Design Principles FTW</a> - "The biggest collection of Design Principles on the Internet."</li>
<li><a href="https://principles.adactio.com/">principles.adactio.com</a> - Huge list with various types of more traditional design principles.</li>
<li><a href="http://bokardo.com/principles-of-user-interface-design/">Principles of User Interface Design</a> - Long list with well explained principles by Joshua Porter</li>
